title: SALLY FITZGIBBONS - 2012 AUSTRALIAN OPEN OF SURFING WOMEN'S CHAMPION
description:
Hurley -- Australian Open of Surfing -- Manly 2012 -- Day 9
What broken wrist? A sore Sally Fitzgibbons, and reigning US Open champion, pushed through the pain barrier to become the first ever Australian Open of Surfing women's champion at her home contest. And the crowd goes nuts.
